about Chris Kanew,

01:13.920 --> 01:14.920
and how he quit,

01:14.960 --> 01:16.154
and all the things he said.

01:19.000 --> 01:21.560
Brad, I loved working
with you so much,

01:21.640 --> 01:24.916
and I learned a lot from you,
but this job has made me...

01:25.920 --> 01:27.353
kind of depressed.

01:27.600 --> 01:30.160
I thought about
how I'd taught this kid everything I knew,

01:30.560 --> 01:32.039
and how he was my only employee,

01:32.120 --> 01:34.953
