11:49.000 --> 11:50.513
Let's fly business, okay?

11:51.120 --> 11:52.120
Really?
Yeah.

11:52.880 --> 11:54.029
Okay. Cool.

11:54.480 --> 11:56.391
I, uh, I never flown business.

11:57.480 --> 11:59.118
Let's make this fucking special, okay?

